---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<MainLayout 
  title="Home | Molecular Virology Lab"
  description="Decoding Virus Pathogenesis — Investigating HIV-1 molecular biology and genetic evolution at SP College Srinagar."
>
  <Navigation />

  <section class="hero-stage">
    <div class="glow-bg-orb"></div>
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="institution-badge">
        <span class="pulse-dot"></span> DEPARTMENT OF BIOCHEMISTRY, S.P. COLLEGE
      </div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        MOLECULAR <span class="text-gradient">VIROLOGY</span> LAB
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Decoding Virus Pathogenesis</p>
      <p class="hero-desc">Investigating HIV-1 molecular biology and genetic evolution with advanced structural modeling.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#quest" class="btn-primary">EXPLORE THE QUEST</a>
        <a href="mailto:muzafarjan@gmail.com" class="btn-secondary">GET IN TOUCH</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="matrix-section">
    <div class="matrix-grid max-width-wrapper">
      <div class="matrix-card">
        <h3>TARGET</h3>
        <p class="matrix-stat">HIV-1</p>
        <p class="matrix-label">Primary Research Focus</p>
      </div>
      <div class="matrix-card">
        <h3>COMPLEX</h3>
        <p class="matrix-stat text-emerald">gp120</p>
        <p class="matrix-label">Glycan Structural Mapping</p>
      </div>
      <div class="matrix-card">
        <h3>PLATFORM</h3>
        <p class="matrix-stat text-blue">3D</p>
        <p class="matrix-label">Interactive Vector Analytics</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="viewer-section max-width-wrapper">
    <div class="section-label">INTERACTIVE VECTOR MATRIX</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">HIV-1 gp120: CD4 Complex</h2>
    
    <div class="glass-viewer-frame">
      <div id="mol-canvas" class="canvas-container"></div>
      
      <div class="viewer-controls">
        <button class="control-btn active" data-style="cartoon">Cartoon</button>
        <button class="control-btn" data-style="surface">Surface</button>
        <button class="control-btn" data-style="spacefill">Spacefill</button>
        <div class="control-divider"></div>
        <button class="control-btn highlight" data-highlight="cd4">CD4 Binding Loop</button>
        <button class="control-btn highlight" data-highlight="phe43">Phe43 Pocket</button>
        <button class="control-btn highlight" data-highlight="v3">V3 Loop</button>
      </div>
      
      <div class="viewer-instruction">
        <span>🖱️ Drag to rotate • Scroll to zoom</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="quest" class="mission-section max-width-wrapper">
    <div class="grid-2col">
      <div class="mission-text-block">
        <span class="section-label">OUR MISSION</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">The Molecular Quest</h2>
        <p>At the heart of the MJ's Lab lies a deep curiosity about viruses. Led by <strong>Dr. Muzafar Jan</strong>, our team is dedicated to pushing the boundaries of scientific understanding, primarily focused on studying HIV-1.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 16px;">Our research focuses on the intersection of molecular biology and virological techniques to explore HIV's glycan structures, genetic variability, and host interactions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-container">
        <div class="quote-card">
          <span class="quote-mark">“</span>
          <blockquote>Where molecules meet meaning.</blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="cinematic-footer">
    <div class="max-width-wrapper footer-content">
      <p>© 2026 Molecular Virology Lab. Department of Biochemistry, Sri Pratap (SP) College Srinagar.</p>
      <p class="credits">Created by <a href="https://bhatmohsin.netlify.app" target="_blank">Bhat Mohsin</a></p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  :root {
    --bg-dark: #030712;
    --card-glass: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.4);
    --border-glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    --neon-blue: #38bdf8;
    --neon-emerald: #34d399;
  }

  body {
    background-color: var(--bg-dark);
    color: #f3f4f6;
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  .max-width-wrapper {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .hero-stage {
    position: relative;
    padding: 160px 24px 100px;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .glow-bg-orb {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10%;
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.08) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 70%);
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .institution-badge {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: #9ca3af;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .pulse-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--neon-blue);
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--neon-blue);
  }

  .hero-title {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 24px 0 16px;
  }

  .text-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--neon-blue), var(--neon-emerald));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.75rem);
    color: #e5e7eb;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
    color: #9ca3af;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: white;
    color: black;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
    color: white;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .matrix-section {
    padding: 40px 0 80px;
  }

  .matrix-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .matrix-card {
    background: var(--card-glass);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    transition: border-color 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .matrix-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .matrix-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: #6b7280;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .matrix-stat {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .text-emerald { color: var(--neon-emerald); }
  .text-blue { color: var(--neon-blue); }

  .matrix-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #9ca3af;
  }

  .viewer-section {
    padding: 60px 24px 100px;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--neon-blue);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .glass-viewer-frame {
    position: relative;
    background: #090d16;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }

  .canvas-container {
    width: 100%;
    height: 550px;
    background-color: #020408;
  }

  .viewer-controls {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    left: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(3, 7, 18, 0.8);
    padding: 6px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    z-index: 20;
  }

  .control-btn {
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    color: #9ca3af;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .control-btn:hover {
    color: white;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  }

  .control-btn.active {
    background: white;
    color: black;
  }

  .control-divider {
    width: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    margin: 4px 6px;
  }

  .control-btn.highlight:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(56,189,248,0.3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.4);
    color: var(--neon-blue);
  }

  .viewer-instruction {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    background: rgba(3, 7, 18, 0.6);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }

  .mission-section {
    padding: 80px 24px 140px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
  }

  .grid-2col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .mission-text-block p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #9ca3af;
  }

  .quote-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .quote-card {
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.01) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
    padding: 48px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: 30px;
    font-size: 5rem;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .quote-card blockquote {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #e5e7eb;
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .cinematic-footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
    padding: 40px 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #4b5563;
  }

  .footer-content {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .credits a {
    color: #9ca3af;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .credits a:hover {
    color: var(--neon-blue);
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .matrix-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .grid-2col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .footer-content { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
